2 thousand (50,000) people or less according to the
3 latest Federal Decennial Census; and
4 4. The Secretary of Commerce, or his or her designee, who shall
5 serve as chair.
6 B. Five members of the Board shall constitute a quorum, and the
7 vote of the majority of members present shall be necessary for any
8 action to be taken by the Board. No vacancy in the membership of
